### Please describe the problem.
Syncing content to an rsync remote no longer works on macOS 26.3.
(Specifically an encrypted rsync remote with shared encryption)

### What steps will reproduce the problem?
MacOS 26.3 (with openrsync)
run: `git annex sync my-rsync-remote --content`
observe: `rsync error: unexpected end of file.`
(these files are all fine and can be opened locally)

### What version of git-annex are you using? On what operating system?
MacOS 26.3 with git-annex from homebrew

