### Have you had any luck using git-annex before? (Sometimes we get tired of reading bug reports all day and a lil' positive end note does wonders)
Yeah was working great for syncing and archiving large static files across multiple drives and machines. (helps deduping them too)
Have also had success in the past syncing to NAS storage using rsync remote and then using it to pull data on demand when away from home.
Thanks for taking the time to read this.
